title: Ghana ace Sulley Muntari returns to training with Al Ittihad Jeddah
text:
Sports News | 14 October 2015 21:10 CET Ghana ace Sulley Muntari returns to training with Al Ittihad Jeddah - www.ghanasoccernet.com Sulley Muntari returns to training with Al Ittihad. 
Ittihad Jeddah ace Sulley Muntari has returned to training after suffering an injury three weeks ago during a Saudi Pro League match. 
Muntari limped off on 18 minutes as Ittihad played hosts to against Al Faisaly.
